dcterms:description: The OLIVES dataset contains 78108 Optical Coherence Tomography (OCT) scans from two clinical trials, with clinical information such as Eye identity, Best Central Visual Acuity (BCVA), and Central Subfield Thickness (CST) collected during patient treatment. A subset of 9408 images is labeled for the presence or absence of 16 different biomarkers.
